### mysql安装
```
yum -y install http://www.percona.com/downloads/percona-release/redhat/0.1-4/percona-release-0.1-4.noarch.rpm && yum  -y install Percona-Server-server-56
或
yum -y install http://www.percona.com/downloads/percona-release/redhat/0.1-4/percona-release-0.1-4.noarch.rpm
yum list | grep percona
yum -y install Percona-Server-server-57
具体过程：https://www.percona.com/doc/percona-server/LATEST/installation/yum_repo.html

二进制安装：
https://blog.csdn.net/jianiuqi/article/details/53502853
```

